/*------------------------------------------------------------------ 
 MBlue Combine Home-Button XP (Ver. 0.1.0)
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Author: M.BLUE - Tested on: Firefox 3.0.5 - Last Update: 27.01.2009
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Description:
 1. Integrates with the "Combine Nav-Buttons XP" style to
    combine the Home-Button with the Back/Forward/Stop/Reload
    buttons.
 2. Gives the same look as the Back/Forward Buttons (Firefox on
    Vista) to the Home-Button.
 3. Supports both SMALL and LARGE Icons.
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Notes:
-YOU NEED THE "COMBINE NAV-BUTTONS XP" STYLE TO MAKE THIS WORKS.

-To make it works, place the buttons in this order:

 > (BACK|FORWARD) (STOP) (RELOAD) (HOME) <

-In customizing mode you'll see the button's background GREEN if
 the position is right, or RED if it's wrong.

-When using THEMES/EXTENSIONS/STYLES that changes some margins, you
 may need to change some value manually, if so go to bottom of the
 page to customize.
--------------------------------------------------------------------
CUSTOMIZING:

 1. NAV-BUTTONS MARGINS.
 2. HOME-BUTTON MARGINS.

> GO TO BOTTOM OF THE PAGE TO CUSTOMIZE
--------------------------------------------------------------------
List of compatible Styles:
[1] Combine Nav-Buttons Vista
[2] Combine Nav-Buttons XP
[3] Nav-Buttons Vista on XP
[4] Nav-Buttons XP on Vista
[5] Combine Home-Button Vista
[6] Combine Home-Button XP (THIS)

How to:
[A] You are on Vista and want to combine the Buttons (BLUE):
    > use styles [1]
[B] You are on XP and want to combine the Buttons (GREEN):
    > use styles [2]
[C] You are on XP and want the Vista Buttons (BLUE):
    > use styles [3]
[D] You are on XP and want both the Vista Buttons and combine:
    > use styles [1] [3]
[E] You are on Vista and want the XP Buttons (GREEN):
    > use styles [4]
[F] You are on Vista and want both the XP Buttons and combine:
    > use styles [2] [4]

[!] You can combine the Home-Button too by using style [5] or [6]
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Integrates with:
 MBlue Combine Nav-Buttons XP
>MBlue Combine Home-Buttons XP
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Updates:
 27.01.2009 Ver. 0.1.0 = done
------------------------------------------------------------------*/



@namespace url(http://www.mozilla.org/keymaster/gatekeeper/there.is.only.xul);

/*******************************************************************
 ADJUST FORWARD & BACK BUTTONS
*******************************************************************/

#main-window #navigator-toolbox toolbar[mode="icons"] #forward-button {
margin: 0px 0px 0px 52px !important;
}

#main-window #navigator-toolbox toolbar[mode="icons"] #back-button {
margin: 0 !important;
}



/*******************************************************************
 HOME BUTTON SETTINGS
*******************************************************************/

#main-window #navigator-toolbox toolbar[iconsize="small"][mode="icons"] #home-button {
-moz-appearance: none !important;
-moz-border-radius: 0px !important;
list-style-image: none !important;
border: none !important;
outline: none !important;
padding: 0 !important;
margin: 0 !important;
min-height: 24px !important;
max-height: 24px !important;
min-width: 26px !important;
max-width: 26px !important;
}

#main-window #navigator-toolbox toolbar[iconsize="large"][mode="icons"] #home-button {
-moz-appearance: none !important;
-moz-border-radius: 0px !important;
list-style-image: none !important;
border: none !important;
outline: none !important;
padding: 0 !important;
margin: 0 !important;
min-height: 34px !important;
max-height: 34px !important;
min-width: 26px !important;
max-width: 26px !important;
}



/*******************************************************************
 REDESIGN HOME BUTTON SMALL
*******************************************************************/

#main-window #navigator-toolbox toolbar[iconsize="small"][mode="icons"] 
#home-button {
background: transparent 
url("data:image/png;base64,") no-repeat center center !important;
}

#main-window #navigator-toolbox toolbar[iconsize="small"][mode="icons"] 
#home-button:hover {
background: transparent 
url("data:image/png;base64,") no-repeat center center !important;
}

#main-window #navigator-toolbox toolbar[iconsize="small"][mode="icons"] 
#home-button:hover:active {
background: transparent 
url("data:image/png;base64,") no-repeat center center !important;
}



/*******************************************************************
 REDESIGN HOME BUTTON LARGE
*******************************************************************/

#main-window #navigator-toolbox toolbar[iconsize="large"][mode="icons"] #home-button {
background: transparent 
url("data:image/png;base64,") no-repeat center center !important;
}

#main-window #navigator-toolbox toolbar[iconsize="large"][mode="icons"] 
#home-button:hover {
background: transparent 
url("data:image/png;base64,") no-repeat center center !important;
}

#main-window #navigator-toolbox toolbar[iconsize="large"][mode="icons"] 
#home-button:hover:active {
background: transparent 
url("data:image/png;base64,") no-repeat center center !important;
}



/*******************************************************************
 ADJUST BUTTONS WHEN CUSTOMIZING
*******************************************************************/

#main-window #navigator-toolbox toolbar[mode="icons"] #wrapper-stop-button #stop-button,
#main-window #navigator-toolbox toolbar[mode="icons"] #wrapper-reload-button #reload-button,
#main-window #navigator-toolbox toolbar[mode="icons"] #wrapper-unified-back-forward-button #back-button,
#main-window #navigator-toolbox toolbar[mode="icons"] #wrapper-unified-back-forward-button #forward-button,
#main-window #navigator-toolbox toolbar[mode="icons"] #wrapper-home-button #home-button {
visibility: visible !important;
margin: 0 !important;
}

#main-window #navigator-toolbox toolbar[mode="icons"] #wrapper-unified-back-forward-button,
#main-window #navigator-toolbox toolbar[mode="icons"] #wrapper-unified-back-forward-button + #wrapper-stop-button,
#main-window #navigator-toolbox toolbar[mode="icons"] #wrapper-unified-back-forward-button + #wrapper-stop-button + 
#wrapper-reload-button,
#main-window #navigator-toolbox toolbar[mode="icons"] #wrapper-unified-back-forward-button + #wrapper-stop-button + 
#wrapper-reload-button + #wrapper-home-button {
background: rgba(0,255,0,0.5) !important;
}

#main-window #navigator-toolbox toolbar[mode="icons"] #wrapper-stop-button,
#main-window #navigator-toolbox toolbar[mode="icons"] #wrapper-reload-button,
#main-window #navigator-toolbox toolbar[mode="icons"] #wrapper-reload-button + #wrapper-unified-back-forward-button,
#main-window #navigator-toolbox toolbar[mode="icons"] #wrapper-stop-button + #wrapper-unified-back-forward-button,
#main-window #navigator-toolbox toolbar[mode="icons"] #wrapper-unified-back-forward-button + #wrapper-reload-button,
#main-window #navigator-toolbox toolbar[mode="icons"] #wrapper-reload-button + #wrapper-stop-button,
#main-window #navigator-toolbox toolbar[mode="icons"] #wrapper-home-button {
background: rgba(255,0,0,0.5) !important;
}











/*=========================[CUSTOMIZE]============================*/



#main-window #navigator-toolbox toolbar[iconsize="small"][mode="icons"] #reload-button,
#main-window #navigator-toolbox toolbar[iconsize="small"][mode="icons"] #stop-button {



/*------------------------------------------------------------------
[1a] STOP & RELOAD BUTTONS MARGINS (SMALL ICONS)

Change the following values if the button's margins are wrong (it
may happen when using different themes/extensions/styles).
------------------------------------------------------------------*/
  margin-left: -91px !important;
  margin-right: 0px !important;
/*----------------------------------------------------------------*/
  margin-top: 1px !important;
  margin-bottom: 1px !important;}
/*----------------------------------------------------------------*/



#main-window #navigator-toolbox toolbar[iconsize="large"][mode="icons"] #reload-button,
#main-window #navigator-toolbox toolbar[iconsize="large"][mode="icons"] #stop-button {



/*------------------------------------------------------------------
[1b] STOP & RELOAD BUTTONS MARGINS (LARGE ICONS)

Change the following values if the button's margins are wrong (it
may happen when using different themes/extensions/styles).
------------------------------------------------------------------*/
  margin-left: -96px !important;
  margin-right: 0px !important;
/*----------------------------------------------------------------*/
  margin-top: 1px !important;
  margin-bottom: 1px !important;}
/*----------------------------------------------------------------*/



#main-window #navigator-toolbox toolbar[iconsize="small"][mode="icons"] #home-button {



/*------------------------------------------------------------------
[2a] HOME-BUTTON MARGINS (SMALL ICONS)

Change the following values if the button's margins are wrong (it
may happen when using different themes/extensions/styles).
Change the right margin to give the Nav-buttons more/less space.
------------------------------------------------------------------*/
  margin-right: 42px !important;
/*----------------------------------------------------------------*/
  margin-top: 1px !important;
  margin-bottom: 1px !important;}
/*----------------------------------------------------------------*/



#main-window #navigator-toolbox toolbar[iconsize="large"][mode="icons"] #home-button {



/*------------------------------------------------------------------
[2b] HOME-BUTTON MARGINS (LARGE ICONS)

Change the following values if the button's margins are wrong (it
may happen when using different themes/extensions/styles).
Change the right margin to give the Nav-buttons more/less space.
------------------------------------------------------------------*/
  margin-right: 47px !important;
/*----------------------------------------------------------------*/
  margin-top: 0px !important;
  margin-bottom: 0px !important;}
/*----------------------------------------------------------------*/



/* END */
